<h1>ASP.NET MVC IoC Demo</h1>

<p>
    This page sends a request to the controller, and the controller uses the repository
    registered in <code>Program.cs</code> through dependency injection.
</p>

<form action="/Positions/Add" method="post">
    <label for="positionName">Position name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="positionName" name="positionName" />
    <button type="submit">Add</button>
</form>

<p>
    <a href="/Positions/List">Open the stored positions</a>
</p>
